OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man accused of breaking Covid-19     
OL,6, restrictions by attending a vigil for  
OL,7, Sarah Everard says he heard of his     
OL,8, conviction "from a news report".       
OL,10,FKevin Godin-Prior, 68, from Manchester,
OL,11,Ftold a court postal delays meant he was
OL,12,Fsent a notice of prosecution two days  
OL,13,Fafter the deadline to respond.         
OL,15,FHe was convicted in his absence under  
OL,16,Fthe Single Justice Procedure on 1 June.
OL,18,FThe conviction has now been dropped    
OL,19,Fafter an appeal against it and Mr      
OL,20,FGodin-Prior pleaded not guilty.        
